title: Starbucks Hype Beasts, Senate Dinosaurs Finally Get it? 10.6.21

description:
In episode 1003, Jack and Miles are joined by writer and comedian Joey Clift to discuss how hospitals weren't bluffing with their vaccine mandates, does congress finally understanding Facebook? Starbucks Stans and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Joey's "How to Cope with Your Team Changing Its Native American Mascot" Video
  2. Hospitals weren’t bluffing, get VAXX’d or GET FUKT
  3. Maybe Frances Haugen can convince Congress to do something this time
  4. Starbucks Stans
  5. LISTEN: AJRadico - "Armore"
